<p><span class="anchor" id="p41"></span>لاشْتِرَاط الْعدَد فِي الْمُقَوّم<a href="#p41" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p42"></span>والا فقاسم<a href="#p42" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
